  "text": "A hyperelastic isotropic material was used to describe myocardium behavior and its parameters were computed from myocardium tensile test. General contact formulation between wire and heart tissue was setup with a 0.005 friction coefficient based on the work of [CITATION_1] . Myocardium and PTFE pledget were tied to simplify model contact.",
